ickmaker and church warden who filled nearly every town office, he sat in the Connecticut house in 1854 — then again in 1884 and 1885, three decades later. He led the firm I. L. Stiles & Son into his late sixties."},{"number":2,"category":"marriage","header":"He married a Hooker cousin without the name","body":"His first wife, Sophronia Blakeslee, turned out to descend from the same Stiles-Hooker root he did, through a different daughter — a cousin match neither surname revealed."}],"quotes":[],"sources":[{"label":"Stiles book (BIB008) #950/#603"},{"label":"FindAGrave 126791136","url":"https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/126791136/isaac_lorenzo-stiles"}],"research_sources":[{"bib_id":"BIB008"}],"documents":[],"slug":"isaac-stiles-1819"},"HD3948":{"id":"HD3948","former_ids":["I00525"],"is_placeholder":false,"has_descendants_documented":true,"bio":{"first_name":"Sophronia","middle_name":"Maria","last_name":"Stiles","maiden_name":"Blakeslee","married_names":["Stiles"],"gender":"female","display_name":"Sophronia Maria Blakeslee Stiles","bio_blurb":"New Haven bride of a Hooker cousin"},"birth":{"year":1819,"month":2,"day":16,"city":"North Haven","county":"New Haven","state":"Connecticut","country":"United States"},"baptism":{},"death":{"year":1886,"month":11,"day":17,"city":"North Haven","county":"New Haven","state":"Connecticut","country":"United States"},"residence":{},"burial":{"cemetery_id":"CEM293"},"classification":{"is_thomas_descendant":true,"is_talcott_descendant":false,"is_thomas_spouse":false,"is_talcott_spouse":false,"generation_from_thomas":8,"include_in_path_calculation":true,"descent_paths_to_thomas":1,"descent_from_thomas_hooker":true,"is_progenitor":false,"is_easter_egg":false},"notable":{"is_notable":false,"notable_category":[]},"parents":{"father_id":"I00531","mother_id":"H01162","father_research_notes":"Daughter of Anson Blakeslee + Julia (Frost) Blakeslee. Per Stiles book #950: 'Julia, dau of Titus and Mabel Frost' — Julia IS our existing H01162 Julia Frost Blakeslee! Sophronia is herself gen 7 Hooker descendant via H01162 → H00448 Mabel Stiles Frost branch. Marriage to Isaac Lorenzo Stiles (HD3934, gen 7 via Mary Stiles H00452 branch) is a Hooker-Hooker cousin marriage between two different branches of Esther Hooker → Rev. Isaac Stiles. Sophronia will be RECLASSIFIED to HD-prefix in Stage 6Y-43 after H01162 Julia is enriched with full child list. Built here as I-spouse with cousin_marriage tag."},"number_of_marriages":1,"marriages":[{"marriage_number":1,"spouse_id":"HD3934","date_year":1842,"date_month":2,"date_day":16,"location_city":"North Haven","location_state":"Connecticut","location_country":"United States","end_type":"death","end_year":1886,"children_ids":["HD3938","HD3939"]}],"education":[],"career":[],"military_service":[],"institutions":[],"landmarks":[],"naming_inspiration":[],"artworks":[],"tags":["cousin_marriage"],"research_tags":[],"cross_connections":[],"narrative_blocks":[{"number":1,"category":"marriage","header":"Wed Isaac Lorenzo on her 23rd birthday, 1842","body":"Sophronia Maria Blakeslee was born February 16, 1819 in North Haven Connecticut; on her 23rd birthday — February 16, 1842 — she married Isaac Lorenzo Stiles in the same town. Their union joined two branches of Esther Hooker's descendants: Sophronia descended through the Mabel Stiles Frost line, Isaac Lorenzo through the Mary Stiles Mansfield line."},{"number":2,"category":"marriage","header":"She married on her twenty-third birthday","body":"On February 16, 1842 — her birthday — she wed Isaac Lorenzo Stiles, born the same year as she. The match joined two branches of the Esther Hooker line, a cousin marriage that doubled their sons’ descent."}],"quotes":[],"sources":[{"label":"FindAGrave 126791203","url":"https://www.findagrave.com/memorial/126791203/sophronia_maria-stiles"}],"research_sources":[{"bib_id":"BIB008"}],"documents":[],"slug":"sophronia-stiles-1819"},"HD3938":{"id":"HD3938","former_ids":[],"is_placeholder":false,"has_